<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/886419-when-i-read-the-book-i-was-reading-an">When I read the book, I was reading an individual experience, not a comment on Islam or the women of Islam; or even Iran. It&#39;s Betty&#39;s experience, and the hatred she describes towards her in-laws is stemming from her plight. I totally get it. It&#39;s a story, not a revolution. Good Read, and a great movie. Thoughts?</a>
</div>
