<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">If I would have been kidnapped by my husband to another country and pretty much his whole family (which is huge) would let it happen and continue, I w<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">If I would have been kidnapped by my husband to another country and pretty much his whole family (which is huge) would let it happen and continue, I would probably hate them too and it would be a very small step to extrapolate this hate to the whole nation. <br /><br /><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
