        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2517187705" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15234933016098446866">I&apos;ve read this maybe 20 years ago, when I was a teenager. Based on my gut, I&apos;d give it 4 stars. Because to this day I remember the book, and I remember how terrified I felt reading it. It left an impression. It&apos;s had an impact.<br/><br/>However, I&apos;ve seen issues raised concerning racism etc. which makes me not want to re-read it, and I decided to not give it a rating.</span>
  <span id="freeText15234933016098446866" style="display:none">I've read this maybe 20 years ago, when I was a teenager. Based on my gut, I'd give it 4 stars. Because to this day I remember the book, and I remember how terrified I felt reading it. It left an impression. It's had an impact.<br /><br />However, I've seen issues raised concerning racism etc. which makes me not want to re-read it, and I decided to not give it a rating.</span>
